sentence: Looking at units outstanding versus one week prior within the universe of ETFs covered at ETF Channel, the biggest outflow was seen in the Consumer Discretionary Select Sector SPDR Fund ( XLY ), where 6,400,000 units were destroyed, or a 4.8% decrease week over week.
Among the largest underlying components of XLY, in morning trading today Amazon.com ( AMZN ) is off about 8.2%, and Home Depot ( HD ) is lower by about 3.1%.

And on a percentage change basis, the ETF with the biggest outflow was the iShares PHLX Semiconductor ETF ( SOXX ), which lost 2,750,000 of its units, representing a 32.2% decline in outstanding units compared to the week prior.
Among the largest underlying components of SOXX, in morning trading today Broadcom ( AVGO ) is off about 4.4%, and Qualcomm (QCOM) is lower by about 2%.
